2. Barry Levinson ( age: 75 ) ( Actor, director, screenwriter, producer )

Barry Levinson (born April 6, 1942) is an American screenwriter, film director, actor, and producer of film and television. His films include Bugsy, The Natural and Rain Man.

3. Barry Roche ( age: 35 ) ( Footballer )

Barry Christopher Roche (born 6 April 1982) is an Irish footballer who plays for Morecambe as a goalkeeper. nicknamed "butterfingers", He is a former Irish Under-21 international.

4. Bartoloměj Kuru ( age: 30 )

Bartoloměj Kuru (born April 6, 1987, in Nymburk) is an Austrian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for First Vienna FC.

5. Beatrice Capra ( age: 25 )
